{"tid":1396126,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Reke Bucsi 近代著名德國動畫家","createTime":"2019-08-02T03:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T18:24:24.000Z","uid":78390,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"863f29fbbfbaa4e5c6012d267a2e0234b95ba06e","tid":1396126,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:50:16.000Z","msg":"最近愛上睇animation short<br />\n因為時間原因 Animation short 比較著中於情感同意境 加上animation俾到電影人創造沒有限制嘅世界 所以劇情往往意想不到<br />\n<br />\n係呢到想介紹Reke Bucsi 一名德國動畫家<br />\n只係用咗三部短動畫已經係電視界打出一個名堂<br />\n係佢嘅世界所有野都荒唐而帶點滑稽<br />\n想睇戲又冇咩時間 Reke嘅動畫不祊試試<br />\n<br />\nSymphony No.42 (2014) 10mins<br />\n呢部探討人同大自然嘅自相矛盾嘅關係<br />\n一方面人愛動物 另一方面人都會無意中傷害大自然<br />\n透過42幅畫作可以見到每幅都耐人尋味畫面<br />\n令人反思人與大自然能否共和<br />\n呢部係本人最愛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rwc9T8H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwc9T8H.png&h=fa449feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHTtqfD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHTtqfD.png&h=fac7e4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLove (2016) 14mins<br />\n應該係我睇過最美嘅動畫<br />\n由宇宙到怪物到小貓<br />\n每個都有自己嘅愛情故事<br />\n由生機到熱戀到分離<br />\n故事抽像帶出愛嘅經歷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CjCt9HA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjCt9HA.png&h=3cca5c7b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vda3YAV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvda3YAV.png&h=e91ab900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSolar Walk (2018) 21mins<br />\n最近作品探索存在論<br />\n究竟係呢個浩瀚宇宙 究竟我地嘅存在係代表啲咩？<br />\n巧妙地用動畫去解答呢個問題<br />\n夢幻 離奇 深化<br />\n完美演繹動畫潛力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oxj8qgf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxj8qgf.png&h=b838d5ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXkLsuB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXkLsuB.png&h=46d5a2fa&s={SIZE}\" />[/b]<br />\n<br />\n係呢度都介紹最近睇過嘅動畫短片<br />\nPussy (2016) Renata Gasiorowska 9mins<br />\n玩西玩到上電影<br />\n<br />\nSuperbia （2016）Luca T&oacute;th 15mins<br />\n挑戰男女在社會嘅角色<br />\n<br />\nCoda (2013) 9mins<br />\n與死神的對話<br />\n<br />\nDavid Lynch 其實係動畫起家 好夠早期作品都係短動畫<br />\nThe Alpahbet (1968) <br />\nDumbland (2002)<br />\nSix Men Getting Sick (1967)"},{"pid":"9a1313c79eedbc6b9cd73c37fa363904adc9804f","tid":1396126,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"Love (2016) <br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/316874134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F316874134&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjJsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=4b590920\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/316874134</a><br />\n<br />\nSymphony No.42 (2014)<br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/153887315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F153887315&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjJsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=ec1afb28\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/153887315</a>"},{"pid":"061f600e41f62d8f8e813d8b5d5d47e375cd6341","tid":1396126,"uid":236359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"高質留名"},{"pid":"dade721a70390fb3713c05a6c375446c3cb22979","tid":1396126,"uid":8766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"高質po<br />\n支持"},{"pid":"60828a020424926981aa52c6de208ced66577078","tid":1396126,"uid":232687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:20:06.000Z","msg":"sickball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4434e6793b49d7b085661cee794563eb2fdf1f36","tid":1396126,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:00:10.000Z","msg":"大家睇過咩短動畫都可以介紹下喎<br />\nPixar 個啲我都好鐘意"},{"pid":"6dc12622ee6eeb31f87a78d03f2785bb8ed1695e","tid":1396126,"uid":135636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:54:5